{"tid":1599351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港自治計劃規劃-第一步","createTime":"2019-09-28T02:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T14:30:58.000Z","uid":205482,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e3847b0454cd3ee65df17f793c7f1cc5865a6303","tid":1599351,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:33:07.000Z","msg":"利申:借ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然連登仔禁憎港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就改名 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港自治</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本法賦予香港人高度自治<br />\n如今林鄭否定一國兩制給予港人自治<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要企出黎名正言順奪回自治權</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>香港人要有民選政府，不被中國影響的獨特司法制度及經濟、教育環境。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一堆連登仔話香港自治撚無計劃 剩喺講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家開始 為香港自治鋪路!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>第一步</strong></span> 做好文宣<br />\nAirdrop文宣,連隴牆文宣<br />\n解釋清楚 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港自治喺基本法賦予ge 政府依家卻否認</strong></span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港自治喺理所當然ge</strong></span><br />\n再列明 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">中共如何侵犯香港自治</span></strong><br />\n例如假普選 經商滲透 清洗廣東話文化等等<br />\n然後提起港共做過咩衰嘢 鼓起大家ge怒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與此同時 民間議會方面都有手足準備緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d32c869e8c3c135d6cc4cbc6a58ad4553e057064","tid":1599351,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:33:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"33b285412538c2271b8a8fa632a2ad18f34b06d9","tid":1599351,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqHqyQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqHqyQK.jpg&h=0796b3a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線請留低你嘅DNA!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCHujkN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCHujkN.gif&h=37db3acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Do9jmF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Do9jmF.jpg&h=efc8703c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ys8JoOj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fys8JoOj.png&h=2d0ace40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"16c9c02d81ee87327e121e726ed0c1b3ba2d5ebe","tid":1599351,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cd6a5f7db2281dc6b04e67aacb80eb155c534d","tid":1599351,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:36:21.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53de02a28b3ad4ad65ea23377160992eb908689b","tid":1599351,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:50:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd92fc2c1e867cc66f8ed95b2164294c109a20cb","tid":1599351,"uid":249243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:51:00.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"743c00287c59c7effe888c5e48b9d6411042aa9a","tid":1599351,"uid":205482,"like":0,"disl