tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:43:38.000Z","msg":"中國夠話中英聯合聲明過期啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭係基本法定係中英聯合聲明呀?<br />\n佢話有就有,無就無嫁啦?<br />\n佢話示威者no stake啦,後尾又咪推翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢ON9又唔係第一日,佢話無,大家更加要大大聲咁同佢講,有呀,點解有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攞歷史文件撻佢塊面呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9042e8bc2be4d8629c7bc5ac2a947d7cf20532a","tid":1599351,"uid":265195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇P牌嘅同我推爆佢"},{"pid":"9921c3f04e279f5120f40224296314c9515b3d96","tid":1599351,"uid":47605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:21:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港自治，重建法治</span></span>"},{"pid":"641a511496fd101361ff49532b29b0c0481c4e3d","tid":1599351,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:48:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e461cb9f1e233a6d39022a2fc3a23b57d1e9f0f","tid":1599351,"uid":324885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"期待<br />\n做文宣好事，注意錯別字"},{"pid":"9d06c6042abc6e62d3e1572883efd0247704a603","tid":1599351,"uid":57018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3847b0454cd3ee65df17f793c7f1cc5865a6303","tid":1599351,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:33:07.000Z","msg":"利申:借ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然連登仔禁憎港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就改名 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港自治</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本法賦予香港人高度自治<br />\n如今林鄭否定一國兩制給予港人自治<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要企出黎名正言順奪回自治權</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>香港人要有民選政府，不被中國影響的獨特司法制度及經濟、教育環境。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一堆連登仔話香港自治撚無計劃 剩喺講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家開始 為香港自治鋪路!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>第一步</strong></span> 做好文宣<br />\nAirdrop文宣,連隴牆文宣<br />\n解釋清楚 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港自治喺基本法賦予ge 政府依家卻否認</strong></span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港自治喺理所當然ge</strong></span><br />\n再列明 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">中共如何侵犯香港自治</span></strong><br />\n例如假普選 經商滲透 清洗廣東話文化等等<br />\n然後提起港共做過咩衰嘢 鼓起大家ge怒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與此同時 民間議會方面都有手足準備緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}